The villain is not malice — it's negligence. It's the gap between "we deployed agents" and "we governed agents."

**The Guide: Suprawall**

Suprawall is the guide — the weapon the hero picks up. Not the hero itself. The customer is always the hero. Suprawall enables their success.

Suprawall speaks with authority ("we intercept every tool call deterministically") but serves the hero ("so you can ship agents with confidence").

